long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Streamline AWS is a tool to help remove the many minor inconveniences the Amazon Web Services dashboard has. It aims to solve many small problems that will help make the developers and dev-ops engineers live's easier.

Current list of features:

- Adds a "click to copy" button on the left of each user's sub within Cognito's "user's and groups" tab.
- Adds a "click to copy" button to the right of each user's sub within each user's profile page.

Want a feature added? Request it in my Discord server! https://discord.gg/5KN4uec

Github repository:
https://github.com/AlexzanderFlores/Streamline-AWS
